originalText.text: We found BKA through another student who regularly attends their workshops and classes.  Our daughter first attended the Elizabeth Teeter Audition workshop and she absolutely loved it.  We started private coaching with Kurt shortly after that and we absolutely adore him!  He's given her such great direction, he's helped her prep monologues/scenes and other materials for auditions and showcases.  We also worked with Michael a few times and love him too!  She was signed with a top Talent Agent within days of BKA's Virtual Agent Showcase.  We've been very happy with the coaching offered by BKA. Highly recommend!

originalText.text: I cannot say enough wonderful things about BKA! The coaching our daughter received from Kurt, Brett, and Jeff has exceeded our expectations in every way. The team's care, kindness, professionalism, and industry knowledge are invaluable. Kurt, especially, has gone above and beyond - we are so grateful for this amazing team!

originalText.text:
I cannot begin to say enough great things about owner, Kurt and the BKA team. Over the last year that our daughter has worked with Kurt she has learned and grown SO much in her acting, she has made wonderful industry contacts and her once shy, self-doubting self has become confident and more outgoing. She also signed with both a talent manager and agent, thanks so the BKA showcase! We have Kurt to thank for ALL of this. His kind and encouraging approach has made him a very favorite person in her life and she looks up to him and truly loves the time she spends with him. This has all been over Zoom, which makes it even more impressive that he has been able to make such an impact. When she was able to join a in-person workshop, she had the time of her life and loved working with such talented teachers and students. She still talks about it and asks weekly when she can attend her next workshop with Kurt and team.

Her time with BKA has not just made her a better/more prepared actor, but a more confident and happier kid overall. We couldn’t be happier to have her working with such kind, talented and dedicated teachers!!

originalText.text: I can't say enough about 'Broadway Kids Auditions'!  I am so pleased with the virtual and in-person sessions with Kurt, Eric, Jeff, and Brett!  My daughter, Ava T., has been involved with BKA since 2022.  She has grown so much under their instruction.  She has participated in BKA Workshops and BKA Showcases.  The Summer Broadway Intensive was a Blast, too!!!  Ava worked with professionials in the field and so much more!  Such a fun and educational experience for Ava! Also, she got to spend a week in NYC!!!  They have all helped her to prepare for her college pre-screens for Musical Theater.  Ava has had multiple call backs for live auditions!  So so proud!!! We couldn't have had such success without the coaching and expertise from Kurt, Eric, Jeff, and Brett.  The support and encouragement from BKA is exceptional!!! Thanks for everything, BKA!!!

originalText.text:
We enrolled Aidan in BKA’s Summer Intensive this past July, and we could not be more thrilled with the experience he had.

Aidan’s dream is to sing, dance and act on Broadway, and this program was a pivotal step in learning what it takes to fulfill that dream!

BKA’s Summer Intensive, held in the heart of New York City, was an immersive and enriching experience that exceeded our expectations and here's why:

Comprehensive Curriculum: The program offered a well-rounded curriculum covering everything from vocal exercises to acting workshops and, of course, dance routines from current performers on Broadway. It was evident that the instructors were seasoned professionals who knew how to nurture young talent.

Exceptional Instructors: The instructors were not just talented; they were genuinely passionate about teaching and mentoring the next generation of Broadway performers. They provided valuable insights, guidance, and personal attention to each student.

Igniting Self-Belief: We were excited to see an extraordinary evolution in Aidan’s self-assurance throughout the program. He not only honed his skills but also learned the importance of professionalism, collaboration, and perseverance.

Inspiring Environment: The atmosphere was incredibly supportive and encouraging. Aidan felt safe taking risks and pushed his boundaries creatively. The camaraderie among the participants was heartwarming.

Performance Showcase: The culmination of the program was a spectacular performance showcase, where Aidan had the opportunity to apply what they had learned. It was an unforgettable experience to see him shine on stage, and witnessing him illuminate the stage was an awe-inspiring, unforgettable experience for my husband and me.

Effective and Organized: Kurt and the BKA team behind the scenes were nothing short of amazing, they were responsive to our inquiries and provided clear information from registration to the final performance. It made the entire process stress-free and enjoyable.

In conclusion, the BKA Intensive was a transformative milestone in Aidan’s journey towards his Broadway dreams. It not only equipped him with essential skills but confirmed his love and passion for the performing arts.

I wholeheartedly recommend BKA to parents whose children share the same aspirations. It's an investment in their future that you won't regret.

Aidan has continued his journey with BKA with one of the coaches from the intensive, Eric. He's been inspiring and dedicated to preparing audition materials that showcase his personality and strengths so he is ready to shine if the opportunity arises!

Thank you to Kurt, Eric, Jeff and the entire team at BKA for nurturing young talent and helping dreams take flight!!!
